# Shopify Storefront API Credentials
# Get these from your Shopify Admin > Settings > Apps and sales channels > Develop apps
# Create a new app and configure Storefront API access

VITE_SHOPIFY_STORE_DOMAIN=your-store.myshopify.com
VITE_SHOPIFY_STOREFRONT_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-storefront-access-token-here

# How to switch from dummy data to Shopify:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Fill in your Shopify credentials
# 3. The data provider will automatically detect the credentials and use Shopify API
# 4. Uncomment the Shopify client code in src/lib/data/data-provider.ts
